Package: jinPocketbook
Type: Package
Title: Justice in Numbers Pocketbook R Package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Phil Hall
Maintainer: Phil Hall <philip.hall@justice.gov.uk>
Description: The Justice in Numbers Pocketbook R package provides a set of functions to build a pocketbook containing charts, tables, and summary information taken from the Justice in Numbers website. Justice in Numbers aims to provide users with easy-to-understand visualizations and insights into various aspects of the justice system in England and Wales.
